cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques in wireless mesh networks, which are a type of wireless network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses various ML techniques and their applications, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a secondary category. Additionally, the paper discusses security and fault tolerance, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses QoS, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory).
